    <p>By the time most large Drupal sites have been around for a year or two, they've accumulated a menagerie of content types. Articles, press releases, product pages, reviews, biographies, landing pages, home pages, promo rotators, photo galleries, and more litter the list of content, and making sure they're treated consistently can be a problem.</p>
